{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ODDCORE</strong> is a first person, retro-inspired boomer shooter with roguelike ingredients that is packed with endless, brain-rotting visuals of your bullets exploding everything that they touch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>DEMO FEATURES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">fast-paced first person combat experience with retro liminal aesthetic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 unique weapons and 8 different gadgets for a combination of 112 unique loadouts\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">25 battle arenas, 4 nightmare variants, and 17 secret variants to discover!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 unique entity types + 2 unique bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">sandbox for custom levels (experimental)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ENDLESS replay-ability with tons of random upgrades that makes no two runs the same</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">leaderboard to keep tab of our best runners of course :)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FOR NOW, IF THE ODDCORE IS CALLING YOUR NAME\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong> please read the letter below, thank you\u00a0</strong>\u2193</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>To YOU, YES YOU</strong>,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Congratulation on landing this gig with us! Here is the run down of the job:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> You are now an ODDCORE runner AND you have been employed to protect the core of our memories one variant at a time. <strong>Deploy each run with new loadouts, manage time wisely and eradicate the corrupted hordes from taking over the ODDCORE.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420190/extras/Equip.gif?t=1739371410\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>EQUIP YOURSELF FOR DEPLOYMENT</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump into the ODDCORE with your own load-out, combining a variety of weapons and gadgets. Prove yourself to be the best among us.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420190/extras/Era.gif?t=1739371410\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>ERADICATE CORRUPTED ENTITIES</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Preserving our memories one kill at a time. A bullet a day keeps the ODD away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420190/extras/Eject.gif?t=1739371410\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>EJECT INTO NEW VARIANTS</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Somebody's gotta do the job! BEWARE, some variants can get odd...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420190/extras/Escape.gif?t=1739371410\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>ESCAPE?!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Just kidding, you can take breaks though........ okay that's 10 seconds, GET BACK TO WORK!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">May the ODDCORE find favor upon you! Try doing a better job than the last guy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sincerely,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ODDBALL ODDIE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Warning!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game contains flashing effects that may be unsuitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy or other photosensitive conditions.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420190/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739371410","backgro